title: Predicting NFC Win Totals
description:
Kevin is joined by The Ringer’s Danny Kelly and Steven Ruiz of USA Today’s For the Win to pick the over/under on each NFC team's projected win total.

Host: Kevin Clark
Guest: Danny Kelly and Steven Ruiz
Production Assistant: Isaiah Blakely
Additional Production Supervision: Arjuna Ramgopal
